    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single deficiency (Test conditions, achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) is accepted given the narrow and well-defined COU limited to ASTM F1717 static compression-bending of the non-cannulated 7.5 mm construct. All three QoIs satisfy quantitative acceptance criteria (E/uval <1.96, percent difference <10%) across N=11 specimens at two laboratories. Overall credibility is sufficient to support regulatory submission. Package conforms to ProfileMinimal; signature workflow is pending and will be completed prior to submission.",
